Business Brief -- Midlantic Corp.:
   Subsidiary Set to Be Sold
   As Part of Restructuring
TA Associates is a private equity investment firm with
offices in Boston and Palo Alto, Calif. The management group
is led by William Hirschfeld, Midlantic Home Mortgage's
president and chief executive officer.
   Midlantic Home Mortgage, which operates 13 offices in New
York, New Jersey and Pennsylvania, serviced or subserviced a
portfolio of about $5.3 billion of residential mortgages as
of Dec. 31.